The paper discusses a method for improving the training of recurrent neural networks (RNNs) on sequence processing tasks. This topic is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
